@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 Outbox 消息统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/outbox/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取死信消息列表（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/outbox/dead-letters?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 手动重试单条死信消息（将 {id} 替换为实际消息 ID）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/outbox/dead-letters/123456789/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Length: 0

### 批量重试所有死信消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/outbox/dead-letters/retry-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Length: 0
